Package: ggccc
Type: Package
Title: Convenient plotting function for CCC
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Miguel Julio Rodo
Maintainer: Miguel Julio Rodo <rdxmig002@myuct.ac.za>
Description: Provides a convenient plotting function for plotting the 
	concordance correlation coefficient along with the raw data, 
	the line of best fit and its confidence interval, and the slope
	and intercept of the line of best fit. 
